OL,3,CWeather warning for thunderstorms in
OL,4,Cplace for Cumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued two weather
OL,7,Fwarnings for thunderstorms for Cumbria
OL,8,Fand Southern Scotland.
OL,10,FThe yellow warnings are in place from
OL,11,Fmidnight on Friday until at least 10am
OL,12,Fin Cumbria and for 24 hours north of
OL,13,Fthe border.
OL,15,FHeavy rain is expected in places as
OL,16,Fpart of the disruption with disruption
OL,17,Fbeing felt through the night from
OL,18,FThursday into Friday.
OL,20,FWhat should you expect from the
OL,21,Fweather warning?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
