OL,3,CWeather warning for thunderstorms in
OL,4,Cplace for Cumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FIn a statement the Met Office said:
OL,7,F"Spells of heavy rain and
OL,8,Fthunderstorms initially over northwest
OL,9,FScotland are likely to become more
OL,10,Fwidespread during Friday morning.
OL,12,F"Further thunderstorms and spells of
OL,13,Fheavy rain are possible in the
OL,14,Fafternoon before becoming confined to
OL,15,Fmore northern areas of Scotland later
OL,16,Fin the day.
