OL,3,CWeather warning for thunderstorms in
OL,4,Cplace for Cumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,F"Rainfall amounts will be highly
OL,7,Fvariable but narrow corridors of 20-30
OL,8,Fmm falling in 1 hour and potentially
OL,9,F30-50 mm in 3 hours is possible.
OL,10,FFrequent lightning, large hail (2-4 cm
OL,11,Fdiameter) and locally gusty winds with
OL,12,Fstronger storms."
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
